  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- so he threw-- threw a pair of pants at me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, please go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, how about some food?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he threw a piece of bread at me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he says, go, go upstairs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I thought he meant upstairs, maybe somebody else lives there, and he-- he's going to help me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I come upstairs also, next floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm two stories high now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm looking down again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and I can hear him talking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "By this time, I hear also say, [GERMAN], which means, enter in formation, you know, because in that-- in that particular order, when we went after water, we were in formation of under the orders of, like, at ease, you know?",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But now it's [GERMAN], which means get in formation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You're getting ready to march again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I'm knocking again on the door on the left, right.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody opens.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I see again steps leading to the-- through-- to-- to the ceiling.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I see a trap door on the ceiling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm beginning to touch in the dark again and see if I could, [? you ?] [? know, ?] find a pair-- a set of steps.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
